    <title>创建博客笔记二</title>
    <url>/2020/07/25/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%BA%8C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="春风拂槛露华浓"><a href="#春风拂槛露华浓" class="headerlink" title="春风拂槛露华浓"></a>春风拂槛露华浓</h1><h2 id="Blog的创建过程"><a href="#Blog的创建过程" class="headerlink" title="Blog的创建过程"></a>Blog的创建过程</h2><h3 id="git安装"><a href="#git安装" class="headerlink" title="git安装"></a>git安装</h3><a id="more"></a>
<p>cmd   命令</p>
<p>git查看安装是否完成</p>
<p>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “邮箱地址”</p>
<p>回车保存密匙在默认位置</p>
<p>rsa密匙位置</p>
<p>C:\Users\DY.ssh</p>
<p>id_rsa.pub</p>
<p>密匙放在git官网保存</p>
<p><img src="/other-images/1595419077045.png" alt="1595419077045"></p>
<h3 id="hexo安装（blog模板）"><a href="#hexo安装（blog模板）" class="headerlink" title="hexo安装（blog模板）"></a>hexo安装（blog模板）</h3><p>管理员运行cmd</p>
<p> npm install hexo-cli -g </p>
<p><img src="/other-images/1595419175566.png" alt="1595419175566"></p>
<p>依次完成</p>
<p>blog可以自己设置博客名字</p>
<h3 id="sublime安装（文本编辑器）"><a href="#sublime安装（文本编辑器）" class="headerlink" title="sublime安装（文本编辑器）"></a>sublime安装（文本编辑器）</h3><p>一条龙安装</p>
<p>打开 sublime text 3</p>
<p>把建成的博客目录放在里面</p>
<h3 id="把博客部署到Git上"><a href="#把博客部署到Git上" class="headerlink" title="把博客部署到Git上"></a>把博客部署到Git上</h3><p>komoriBlog目录下cmd</p>
<p>安装插件</p>
<p>npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</p>
<p>hexo g  打包</p>
<p>hexo s -p 5555      开启端口</p>
<p>hexo d  上传</p>
<h3 id="在config-yml文件修改语言"><a href="#在config-yml文件修改语言" class="headerlink" title="在config.yml文件修改语言"></a>在config.yml文件修改语言</h3><p>language： zh-CN</p>
<h3 id="打开标签和分类"><a href="#打开标签和分类" class="headerlink" title="打开标签和分类"></a>打开标签和分类</h3><p>在themes/next的configyml打开</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#about: /about/ || user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">th</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || calendar</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || sitemap</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || heartbeat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后创建标签页和分页</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo n page tags</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo n page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在新建source/tags的index.md</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2020</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-24</span> <span class="number">17</span><span class="string">:06:50</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"tags"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在新建source/categories的index.md</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">分页</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2020</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-24</span> <span class="number">17</span><span class="string">:18:12</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"categories"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="友情链接"><a href="#友情链接" class="headerlink" title="友情链接"></a>友情链接</h3><p>next的config.yml文件</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">links:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h3 id="写博客"><a href="#写博客" class="headerlink" title="写博客"></a>写博客</h3><p>创建博客</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$hexo n 文章名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>书写格式</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 创建博客笔记</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-07-24 18:39:34</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">	- 导航</span><br><span class="line">	- 分享</span><br><span class="line">categories: 笔记</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"># 云想云裳花想容</span><br><span class="line">## hahaha</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="开启打赏功能"><a href="#开启打赏功能" class="headerlink" title="开启打赏功能"></a>开启打赏功能</h3><p>在next的配置文件中</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reward_settings:</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, reward will be displayed in every article by default.</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  animation: false</span><br><span class="line">  comment: 如果文章对你有用，请支持一下哦！</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">reward:</span><br><span class="line">  wechatpay: /images/weixin.png</span><br><span class="line">  alipay: /images/alipay.jpg</span><br><span class="line">  # paypal: /images/weixin.png</span><br><span class="line">  # bitcoin: /images/bitcoin.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="开启订阅公众号"><a href="#开启订阅公众号" class="headerlink" title="开启订阅公众号"></a>开启订阅公众号</h3><p>在next的配置文件中</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">follow_me:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#Twitter: https://twitter.com/username || twitter</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#Telegram: https://t.me/channel_name || telegram</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">WeChat:</span> <span class="string">/images/wechat_channel.jpg</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">wechat</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#RSS: /atom.xml || rss</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="设置头像可旋转"><a href="#设置头像可旋转" class="headerlink" title="设置头像可旋转"></a>设置头像可旋转</h3><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Replace the default image and set the url here.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">/images/pig.jpg</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If true, the avatar will be dispalyed in circle.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rounded:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rotated:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="全文阅读"><a href="#全文阅读" class="headerlink" title="全文阅读"></a>全文阅读</h3><p>打开全文阅读按钮</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Read more button</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># If true, the read more button will be displayed in excerpt section.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">read_more_btn:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在每篇文章添加</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!--</span> <span class="string">more</span> <span class="string">--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="开启背景动画"><a href="#开启背景动画" class="headerlink" title="开启背景动画"></a>开启背景动画</h3><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">canvas_nest:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="修改超链接样式"><a href="#修改超链接样式" class="headerlink" title="修改超链接样式"></a>修改超链接样式</h3><p>themes\next\source\css_common\components\post\post.styl</p>
<p>添加如下样式</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">.post-body</span> <span class="string">p</span> <span class="string">a&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">color:</span> <span class="comment">#2548;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">border-bottom:</span> <span class="string">none;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&amp;:hover&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">color:</span> <span class="string">purple;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="打开不蒜子统计"><a href="#打开不蒜子统计" class="headerlink" title="打开不蒜子统计"></a>打开不蒜子统计</h3><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">busuanzi_count:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_visitors:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_visitors_icon:</span> <span class="string">user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_views:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_views_icon:</span> <span class="string">eye</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_views:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_views_icon:</span> <span class="string">eye</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="增加加载功能"><a href="#增加加载功能" class="headerlink" title="增加加载功能"></a>增加加载功能</h3><p>pace</p>
<h3 id="消除下方版本"><a href="#消除下方版本" class="headerlink" title="消除下方版本"></a>消除下方版本</h3><p>D:\git-for-windows\blog\komoriBlog\themes\next\layout_partials\footer.swig</p>
<p>把下面的注掉</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!--&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">if</span> <span class="string">theme.footer.powered</span> <span class="string">%&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&lt;div</span> <span class="string">class="powered-by"&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">set</span> <span class="string">next_site</span> <span class="string">=</span> <span class="string">'https://theme-next.org'</span> <span class="string">%&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">if</span> <span class="string">theme.scheme</span> <span class="string">!==</span> <span class="string">'Gemini'</span> <span class="string">%&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="string">&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">set</span> <span class="string">next_site</span> <span class="string">=</span> <span class="string">'https://'</span> <span class="string">+</span> <span class="string">theme.scheme</span> <span class="string">|</span> <span class="string">lower</span> <span class="string">+</span> <span class="string">'.theme-next.org'</span> <span class="string">%&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">endif</span> <span class="string">%&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&#123;&#123;-</span> <span class="string">__('footer.powered',</span> <span class="string">next_url('https://hexo.io',</span> <span class="string">'Hexo'</span><span class="string">,</span> <span class="string">&#123;class:</span> <span class="string">'theme-link'</span><span class="string">&#125;)</span> <span class="string">+</span> <span class="string">' &amp; '</span> <span class="string">+</span> <span class="string">next_url(next_site,</span> <span class="string">'NexT.'</span> <span class="string">+</span> <span class="string">theme.scheme,</span> <span class="string">&#123;class:</span> <span class="string">'theme-link'</span><span class="string">&#125;))</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#123;%-</span> <span class="string">endif</span> <span class="string">%&#125;--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="开启字数统计和阅读时长"><a href="#开启字数统计和阅读时长" class="headerlink" title="开启字数统计和阅读时长"></a>开启字数统计和阅读时长</h3><p>安装插件</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-symbols-count-time</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>配置如下</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">symbols_count_time:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">separated_meta:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_post:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_total:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
